Class SuffixesToReplicateOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.quicksetup.installer.SuffixesToReplicateOptions
  • public class SuffixesToReplicateOptions
extends Object
    This class is used to provide a data model for the Suffix to Replicate Options panel of the installer.
